{"tid":133027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁頌昕行李門事件　高院准空姐就機管局決定提司法覆核","createTime":"2017-02-24T09:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T06:48:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e9fdfb584d1002559b1a7e9484fec5a8438677","tid":133027,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/02/judicial-review-of-bag-gate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F02%2Fjudicial-review-of-bag-gate%2F&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=a1ac97f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/02/judicial-review-of-bag-gate/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/0224_leung.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F0224_leung.jpg&h=1532f72b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首幼女梁頌昕去年三月將手提行李遺留在禁區外，獲機管局特事特辦，准許在梁頌昕不親自在場下，由國泰職員代送行李入禁區。香港空勤人員總工會早前派代表就機管局決定申請司法覆核，今日（廿四日）獲高等法院批出申請許可。<br />\n<br />\n代表申請人羅美美的資深大律師李志喜指，《航空保安計劃》清楚列明隨身行李每次都必須在乘客在場下進行安檢，但機管局調查報告的解釋有不同之處。她表示，這個情況會向全球恐佈份子宣傳香港機場有保安大漏洞，申請人作為空中服務員，很多時候要在航機上工作，面對機場保安風險，問題關乎到她的利益。<br />\n<br />\n代表機管局和機場保安公司的律師表示，引起今次訴訟的事件，只是個別事件，是因行李物主身份特殊才提出今次司法覆核。律師指，事件中物主的行李經過多次安檢，最終與物主一起登機，根本無引發保安問題，亦不構成公眾對機場安全的關注，沒有公眾利益的理據進行司法覆核。律師認為，申請人並沒有牽涉入事件中，不適合提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n當局可以就事件通歉認錯，但當局選擇在事後辯解，向全球恐佈份子宣傳香港機場有保安大漏洞，申請人作為空中服務員，每日都在航機上工作，暴露於機場保安風險，問題關乎到她的利益。<br />\n<br />\n法庭今日聽罷雙方陳詞後批出申請許可，案件將排期聆訊。"},{"pid":"441f2257292099c0268adb8fd3fe4e42275d2dbc","tid":133027,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2226c9fd5595bafc376ca6d8d690641eb9bdb93a","tid":133027,"uid":13700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"咁就一年"},{"pid":"12bbe94651ea29b031d3a95a0bd9ac35eed92053","tid":133027,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"996bc6e8040da1a0c6f74611bfc1d1546b840144","tid":133027,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"果然人去茶涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊5千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69adb146f0773779fec139731aeb08f91922aa0b","tid":133027,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fab35f1cfd6d860eda1810044993f676403833","tid":133027,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"96a8e48efabba6cbc602f822fbd17eb73fbcb3b0","tid":133027,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}